import React from "react";
import { Nav, NavLink, NavMenu }
    from "./NavBarElements";


const navTabs = [{
  route: "/",
  icon: "fa fa-home",
  label: "Home",
  },
  {route: "/Music",
  icon: "fa fa-music",
  label: "Music",
  },
  {route: "/Contact",
  icon: "fa fa-envelope",
  label: "Contact",
  },
  {route: "/Shows",
  icon: "fa fa-calendar",
  label: "Shows",
  },
  {route: "/Merch",
  icon: "fa fa-shopping-cart",
  label: "Merch",
  },
  {route: "/About",
  icon: "fa fa-info-circle",
  label: "About",
}]
 
const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Nav>
                <NavMenu>
                    <NavLink to="/" activeStyle>
                        Home
                    </NavLink>
                    <NavLink to="/Music" activeStyle>
                        Music
                    </NavLink>
                    <NavLink to="/Contact" activeStyle>
                        Contact 
                    </NavLink>
                    <NavLink to="/Shows" activeStyle>
                        Shows/Tours
                    </NavLink>
                    <NavLink to="/Merch" activeStyle>
                        Merch
                    </NavLink>
                    <NavLink to="/About" activeStyle>
                        About
                    </NavLink>
                </NavMenu>
            </Nav>
        </>
    );
};
 
export default Navbar;
